properties.Description: Properties of the MDE configuration or data parameter needed to onboard the machine to MDE

onboardingPackageWindows.Description: The onboarding package used to onboard Windows machines to MDE, coded in base64. This can also be used for onboarding using the dedicated VM Extension

onboardingPackageLinux.Description: The onboarding package used to onboard Linux machines to MDE, coded in base64. This can also be used for onboarding using the dedicated VM Extension
